        <item>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2019-01-25T19:40:45Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill terminates certain limitations regarding drug rebates under Medicaid. Currently, the maximum rebate that drug manufacturers must pay under Medicaid for single-source and innovator multiple-source drugs is 100%&nbsp;of the average manufacturer price of the drug. The bill specifies that this limitation only applies to rebate periods that begin before January 1, 2019. </p>]]></text>
